            <title>[LU-6743] OUT: improvements to the protocol</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6743</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;OUT protocol can be improved in few cases:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;replace struct obdo with a flexible structure, as the former is ~280bytes&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;encode frequently used EA&apos;s names&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
